<h3 class="title">DRU武器（さるまね企画）&nbsp;<span class="category">[<a href="http://www.miskdou.com/archives/cat_everquest.html">EverQuest</a>]</span></h3>
<p>便乗企画、UberDRUは一体何を装備しているのか。<br />
対象はEQRankings.comでHP上位100キャラです。</p>

<blockquote class="monospace">
<div>77&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=21886" target="_blank">Hammer of Hours</a></div>
<div>&nbsp;7&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=68775" target="_blank">Fleshthreader's Mace</a></div>
<div>&nbsp;5&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=69098" target="_blank">Ixt Bone Scepter</a></div>
